node.text:
Posty Fest 2021 is happening! 
Presale tomorrow 10am CT you can use code PF21 for access. Public on sale is Friday July 30th at 10am CT. The festival will be 2 days this year and completely outdoors:) love you guys we’re so happy to be back @postyfest 💛💛
